\p{I am an \em{Associate Professor in Logical Foundations and Formal Methods} at [University of Cambridge](https://www.cst.cam.ac.uk/people/js2878/). I study programming languages and semantics using type theory, category theory, domain theory, and topos theory as a guide. My other interests include Near Eastern, Classical, and Germanic philology. Find my contact information [here](https://www.cst.cam.ac.uk/people/js2878)}

